he ameliorative effect of trade and foreign direct investment on the global environment."--cProvided by publisher.  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aEnvironmental policyzChina. 0aInternational trade. 0aChinaxEnvironmental conditions. 4aElectronic books.1 aEastin, Joshua.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher. 0aMichigan studies in international political economy40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.2099075